messages.message: Hi :wave: I was chatting with @alagu today. I realize that folks might not know we have style guidance for our voice, tone, UI, capitalization. I crafted a UI styles in brief (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/DOCS/pages/173506637/Technical+content+style+guidance#UI-styles-in-brief) section today. As always, I'm here for all things content. Questions? Please ask.
